	**************************************************
	*						 *
	*	       1.0-7 NEWS			 *
	*						 *
	**************************************************


		CHANGES IN animation VERSION 1.0-7


NEW FEATURES

    o moving.block() to plot a subset of data by blocks
    o ani.options() gained a new argument 'loop' to 
  control the iteration of the animation in an HTML
  page: TRUE to interate for infinite times, and FALSE
  not to interate (only play once). Thanks, Marcin Kozak!

MINOR CHANGES

    o fixed a bug for in ani.stop(): when 
  ani.options(footer = FALSE), ani.stop() will report
  an error for non-existent object 'footer'; I should
  have used the value ani.options("footer") in the code.
  Thanks, Marcin Kozak!


