	**************************************************
	*						 *
	*	       1.0-5 NEWS			 *
	*						 *
	**************************************************


		CHANGES IN animation VERSION 1.0-5


NEW FEATURES

    o new demo 'Sierpinski' for Sierpinski triangle;
  see demo(Sierpinski).
    o ani.options('footer') was changed to allow
  a custom string to be written in the HTML page
  as the footer information. (Thanks, Jorge Nieves)

SIGNIFICANT CHANGES

    o tidy.source2() was merged into tidy.source(),
  and tidy.source() now returns a list of character
  vectors and also gains an argument 'output' to 
  decide whether to output the tidied code (to 
  R console or a file).


